The cost of not having youth and high school athletics this fall will be significant. Sports play an integral role in the health and education of our children. Our kids want to play, and they can do so safely.

@GovPritzker, it’s time to let them play.
https://t.co/1JS90khN5O

Congress should be in DC doing the People’s business, not sitting on the sidelines while essential workers fight #COVIDー19.

@GOPLeader, @RodneyDavis, and @TomColeOK04’s safe, reasonable plan to get Congress back to work is the right approach.
https://t.co/Bw7q8BHZtg
